      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per minute</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.AkV4Jyllo6nlK2Sl]{Cobra Stance}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You lash out with devious intent and the power to envenom your foe. Make a cobra fang Strike. Your reach with this Strike is 5 feet greater than normal.</p>\n<p>If this Strike hits, the target takes @Damage[1d4[persistent,poison]] per weapon damage die.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Special</strong> If you have this feat, the circumstance bonus to Fortitude saves and Fortitude DC granted by Cobra Stance increases from +1 to +2.</p>"
